---- MODULE ParticipantVoiceState ----
\* Voice state machine for a single room participant. Tracks microphone and listening status.
\* Generated by tlaiser — https://github.com/hyperpolymath/tlaiser

EXTENDS Naturals, Sequences, TLC

\* State constants — each represents a distinct state
CONSTANTS Connected, Muted, Deafened, Priority

\* Variables tracked by this specification
VARIABLES state, is_speaking, volume

\* Type invariant: state is always one of the declared states
TypeInvariant == state \in {Connected, Muted, Deafened, Priority}

\* Initial state predicate
Init ==
    /\ state = Connected
    /\ is_speaking = FALSE
    /\ volume = 10

\* Transition actions
\* Transition: Connected -> Muted (self_mute)
self_mute ==
    /\ state = Connected
    /\ state' = Muted
    /\ is_speaking := FALSE
    /\ UNCHANGED <<is_speaking, volume>>

\* Transition: Connected -> Deafened (self_deafen)
self_deafen ==
    /\ state = Connected
    /\ state' = Deafened
    /\ is_speaking := FALSE
    /\ UNCHANGED <<is_speaking, volume>>

\* Transition: Connected -> Priority (grant_priority)
grant_priority ==
    /\ state = Connected
    /\ state' = Priority
    /\ UNCHANGED <<is_speaking, volume>>

\* Transition: Muted -> Connected (self_unmute)
self_unmute ==
    /\ state = Muted
    /\ state' = Connected
    /\ UNCHANGED <<is_speaking, volume>>

\* Transition: Muted -> Deafened (self_deafen)
self_deafen ==
    /\ state = Muted
    /\ state' = Deafened
    /\ UNCHANGED <<is_speaking, volume>>

\* Transition: Deafened -> Connected (self_undeafen)
self_undeafen ==
    /\ state = Deafened
    /\ state' = Connected
    /\ UNCHANGED <<is_speaking, volume>>

\* Transition: Priority -> Connected (revoke_priority)
revoke_priority ==
    /\ state = Priority
    /\ state' = Connected
    /\ UNCHANGED <<is_speaking, volume>>

\* Transition: Priority -> Muted (priority_mute)
priority_mute ==
    /\ state = Priority
    /\ state' = Muted
    /\ UNCHANGED <<is_speaking, volume>>

\* Next-state relation: disjunction of all transitions
Next ==
    \/ self_mute
    \/ self_deafen
    \/ grant_priority
    \/ self_unmute
    \/ self_deafen
    \/ self_undeafen
    \/ revoke_priority
    \/ priority_mute

\* All variables tuple (for stuttering)
vars == <<state, is_speaking, volume>>

\* Complete specification
Spec == Init /\ [][Next]_vars

\* Fair specification (with weak fairness on Next)
FairSpec == Spec /\ WF_vars(Next)

\* ---- Temporal Properties ----
\* Property: MutedParticipantNeverSpeaking (safety)
MutedParticipantNeverSpeaking == []([][ParticipantVoiceState = Muted => ~is_speaking]_ParticipantVoiceState)

\* Property: RoomNeverExceedsMaxParticipants (safety)
RoomNeverExceedsMaxParticipants == []([][participant_count <= max_participants]_participant_count)

\* Property: NegotiationEventuallyCompletes (liveness)
NegotiationEventuallyCompletes == <>(<>(PeerNegotiation = Connected))


====
